( whistle blows )

23
00:03:00,100 --> 00:03:01,833
( yells )

24
00:03:07,100 --> 00:03:09,000
( whistle blows )

25
00:03:26,867 --> 00:03:29,000
( grunting )

26
00:03:32,900 --> 00:03:35,267
PULLO, FORMATION!

27
00:03:35,334 --> 00:03:37,934
- ( screams )
- PULLO!

28
00:03:38,000 --> 00:03:40,067
SINGLE FORMATION!

29
00:03:42,501 --> 00:03:44,934
SHIELDS ON ME!

30
00:04:00,100 --> 00:04:03,301
GET BACK IN FORMATION,
YOU DRUNKEN FOOL.

31
00:04:10,568 --> 00:04:13,434
REFORM!

32
00:04:13,501 --> 00:04:18,900
Man:
LEGIONARY TITUS PULLO
IS A HERO OF THE 13th LEGION,

33
00:04:18,967 --> 00:04:20,767
- BUT LOOK AT HIM NOW.
- ( whip cracking )

34
00:04:20,833 --> 00:04:24,000
JUSTICE KNOWS
EVERY MAN'S NUMBER.

35
00:04:24,067 --> 00:04:26,967
HE HAS COMMITTED
A TERRIBLE SACRILEGE,

36
00:04:27,034 --> 00:04:29,967
AND HE WILL PAY FOR IT
WITH HIS LIFE!

37
00:04:30,034 --> 00:04:34,534
AS WILL ANY MAN HERE
WHO BREAKS THE LAW.

38
00:04:34,601 --> 00:04:37,967
BRAWLERS AND DRUNKARDS
WILL BE FLOGGED.

39
00:04:38,034 --> 00:04:41,167
THIEVES WILL BE STRANGLE

40
00:04:41,234 --> 00:04:45,733
DESERTERS
WILL BE CRUCIFIED.

41
00:04:52,934 --> 00:04:55,000
IS THAT IT?

42
00:04:55,067 --> 00:04:57,434
I WAS JUST BEGINNING
TO ENJOY MYSELF.

43
00:05:11,201 --> 00:05:12,767
Man:
BEFORE YOU...

44
00:05:12,833 --> 00:05:16,201
VERCINGETORIX,
SON OF CELTIL,

45
00:05:16,267 --> 00:05:19,067
CHIEFTAIN OF THE TRIBE
OF THE ARVERNI,

46
00:05:19,134 --> 00:05:22,700
COMMANDER OF THE REBEL
STRONGHOLD OF ELYSIA,

47
00:05:22,767 --> 00:05:24,967
KING OF ALL THE GAULS.

48
00:05:26,067 --> 00:05:28,134
WHAT WOULD YOU
HAVE OF HIM?

49
00:05:49,267 --> 00:05:51,601
- ( unleashes sword )
- CAESAR!

50
00:05:51,668 --> 00:05:53,501
- ( soldiers cheering )
- CAESAR!

51
00:05:53,568 --> 00:05:54,967
CAESAR!

52
00:05:55,034 --> 00:05:59,301
( soldiers chanting )
CAESAR! CAESAR! CAESAR!

53
00:06:16,001 --> 00:06:17,334
HEY!

54
00:06:17,400 --> 00:06:20,167
HEY, WHAT'S GOING ON?

55
00:06:20,234 --> 00:06:22,734
HEY-- HERE!

56
00:06:24,368 --> 00:06:27,433
YOU PISS-DRINKING
SONS OF CIRCUS WHORES!

57
00:06:27,500 --> 00:06:30,400
THE CHIEF OF THE GAULS
HAS SURRENDERED TO CAESAR.

58
00:06:30,467 --> 00:06:32,268
THE WAR IS OVER.

59
00:06:33,600 --> 00:06:36,101
DON'T SATHATY

60
00:06:36,167 --> 00:06:38,034
THE BOYS HAVE BEEN GIVEN
TWO DAYS LIBERTY

61
00:06:38,101 --> 00:06:40,734
TO SACK THE TOWN
AND TAKE PERSONAL SPOILS.

62
00:06:40,800 --> 00:06:43,301
THEY'LL ALL BE RICH.

63
00:06:43,368 --> 00:06:45,400
AND ME IN HERE!

64
00:06:45,467 --> 00:06:47,134
HEY!

65
00:06:51,134 --> 00:06:53,734
- ( woman screaming )
- COME ON, GET IN THERE!

66
00:06:54,934 --> 00:06:57,268
400 DENARII?
ARE YOU INSANE?

67
00:06:57,334 --> 00:06:58,934
THAT'S A FLOOR PRICE.

68
00:06:59,001 --> 00:07:03,001
WE'LL PAY THE USUAL PREMIUM
FOR TRADESMEN AND FERTILE
WOMEN, ET CETERA.

69
00:07:04,201 --> 00:07:05,667
FROM POMPEY MAGNUS, SIR.

70
00:07:05,734 --> 00:07:08,834
Man:
SET THE FLOOR
CLOSEREIGH TO

71
